text: Ninja Warrior UK is a British physical obstacle assault course game show, created for ITV. It was presented by Ben Shephard, Chris Kamara and Rochelle Humes. ==Series overview== Series Start date End date Episodes Top Contestant 1 Tim Shieff 2 Owen McKenzie 3 Jonny Urszuly 4 Tim Shieff 5 Tim Champion == References == Category:2015 television series debuts Category:2019 television series endings
